## 13. IMAGE HANDLING

- All network images use `cached_network_image`; never use `Image.network()` directly.
- Every image must define both `placeholder` and `errorWidget`.
- Placeholders use shimmer matching the real image's aspect ratio.

```dart
CachedNetworkImage(
  imageUrl: user.avatarUrl,
  fit: BoxFit.cover,
  placeholder: (context, url) => ShimmerBox(width: 40, height: 40),
  errorWidget: (context, url, error) => const ImageErrorPlaceholder(),
);
```

- `ShimmerBox` and `ImageErrorPlaceholder` are global widgets in `lib/global_widgets/`.
- PDF thumbnail (first page preview) is generated locally on-device after upload using the `pdfx` package; never loaded from network.

