## 17. DISPOSE / ONCLOSE

- Every `TextEditingController`, `ScrollController`, `AnimationController`, `FocusNode` in a `GetxController` **must** be disposed in `onClose()`.

```dart
@override
void onClose() {
  emailController.dispose();
  passwordController.dispose();
  scrollController.dispose();
  super.onClose(); // always last
}
```

- `super.onClose()` always last.
- Streams / listeners started in `onInit()` must be cancelled in `onClose()`.

