## 19. BINDING NAMING

- Files: snake_case. Classes: PascalCase. Pattern: `[page]_binding.dart` ‚Üí `[Page]Binding`.
- Binding files live in the page's `bindings/` folder.
- Register only that page's controllers and services with `lazyPut`:

```dart
class DocumentDetailBinding extends Bindings {
  @override
  void dependencies() {
    Get.lazyPut<DocumentAnalysisService>(() => DocumentAnalysisServiceGemini());
    Get.lazyPut<MarketDataService>(() => MarketDataServiceImpl());
    Get.lazyPut<DocumentDetailController>(() => DocumentDetailController());
  }
}
```

| File | Class |
|------|-------|
| home_binding.dart | HomeBinding |
| document_upload_binding.dart | DocumentUploadBinding |
| document_detail_binding.dart | DocumentDetailBinding |
| aggregate_binding.dart | AggregateBinding |
| login_binding.dart | LoginBinding |
| register_binding.dart | RegisterBinding |
| settings_binding.dart | SettingsBinding |

