## 21. GENERAL RULES

- Globally shared widgets ‚Üí `lib/global_widgets/`.
- Page-specific widgets ‚Üí that page's `widgets/` folder.
- Prefer `AppConstants` constants over magic numbers.
- Every `GetPage` has a **Binding**; controllers lazy-injected through bindings.
- Every `pubspec.yaml` dependency includes an **English** comment explaining why it was added.
- All in-code comments written in **English**.
- `AppColors.positive` for income / gains / uptrend. `AppColors.negative` for expense / loss / downtrend. Apply consistently ‚Äî never use green/red raw colors outside of these semantics.
- App Store name: **Finnalyze** (no apostrophe ‚Äî App Store does not accept special characters). Visual identity: **Fin'nalyze** with styled apostrophe.

