## 22. GEMINI AGENTIC LAYER ‚Äî HACKATHON CORE

This is the central architecture that earns the Hack3athon'26 Agentic Structures score (10 pts) and powers all AI features.

### The 4 Agents

| Agent | Input | Output | When |
|-------|-------|--------|------|
| `DocumentParserAgent` | PDF bytes (`Uint8List`) | `DocumentAnalysisModel` | After PDF upload |
| `FinancialInsightAgent` | `List<TransactionModel>` + `MarketSnapshotModel` | `InsightModel` | After parsing, enriched with live market data |
| `AggregateAgent` | `List<DocumentAnalysisModel>` | `AggregateAnalysisModel` | When user opens aggregate view |
| `RecommendationAgent` | `InsightModel` + `AggregateAnalysisModel` | `List<RecommendationModel>` | After insight generation |

The agent pipeline for a single document:
```
PDF Upload
  ‚Üí DocumentParserAgent      ‚Üí DocumentAnalysisModel
  ‚Üí MarketDataService        ‚Üí MarketSnapshotModel  (parallel fetch)
  ‚Üí FinancialInsightAgent    ‚Üí InsightModel
  ‚Üí RecommendationAgent      ‚Üí List<RecommendationModel>
```

