### Response Schema Enforcement

- Every Gemini call sets `responseMimeType: 'application/json'` in `GenerationConfig`.
- JSON parsed in the **service layer**. Controllers receive typed models only.
- Malformed JSON ‚Üí service throws `GeminiParseException` ‚Üí controller sets `hasError(true)` ‚Üí view shows localized error.
- Raw Gemini errors are never shown to the user.

### GeminiService Structure

```dart
// lib/services/gemini_service.dart
class GeminiService extends GetxService {
  late final GenerativeModel _model;

  @override
  void onInit() {
    super.onInit();
    _model = GenerativeModel(
      model: 'gemini-1.5-flash',
      apiKey: dotenv.env['GEMINI_API_KEY']!,
      generationConfig: GenerationConfig(responseMimeType: 'application/json'),
    );
  }

  Future<DocumentAnalysisModel> runDocumentParserAgent(Uint8List pdfBytes) async { ... }
  Future<InsightModel> runFinancialInsightAgent(List<TransactionModel> txs, MarketSnapshotModel market) async { ... }
  Future<AggregateAnalysisModel> runAggregateAgent(List<DocumentAnalysisModel> docs) async { ... }
  Future<List<RecommendationModel>> runRecommendationAgent(InsightModel insight) async { ... }
}
```

### MarketDataService ‚Äî Free APIs Only

```dart
// lib/services/market_data_service.dart
class MarketDataService extends GetxService {
  // TCMB ‚Äî Central Bank of Turkey open API (no key required)
  Future<double> fetchUsdTryRate() async { ... }
  Future<double> fetchEurTryRate() async { ... }
  Future<double> fetchInflationRate() async { ... }

  // Exchange Rate API (free tier)
  Future<Map<String, double>> fetchExchangeRates(String baseCurrency) async { ... }

  // Alpha Vantage (free tier: 25 calls/day ‚Äî use sparingly)
  Future<double> fetchStockPrice(String symbol) async { ... }

  // Aggregated snapshot ‚Äî called once per document detail load
  Future<MarketSnapshotModel> fetchMarketSnapshot() async { ... }
}
```

All market data is cached in GetStorage with a 15-minute TTL to stay within free API call limits.
